To Manawatu Families in Generally, Palu said, since the last update written 6 years ago, Palmerston North city has 2884 Fijian nationals based either in Te Awa Kairangi or Te Akitu Chapter.
With purchases from the FMFB’s Te Awa Kairangi branch in 2011/2012 financial year exceeding $65,422, Te Awa Kairangi is ahead of Te Akitu Chapter under Palu.
